---

A sensor platform for Belgian Area.

### Configuration

add this to configuration.yaml

```yaml
  sensor:
  - platform: dynamic_prices
```    
### Options

#### Time between updates
Every day the values are downloaded from the elias platform.
    
<div class='note'>
  every 10 seconds the values are updated internally
</div>
